一个理论：梯度下降法。 用这个方法求出参数的更新量，去更新参数。 参数被更新百万次后，我们认为参数更新完成，即模型训练完成。 这这个过程涉及到巨量的计算。 那有没有模型可以预测出比梯度下降更精准的参数更新量？比如类似神经辐射场，可以想神经梯度空间？低维神经空间再推广到高维神经空间？ 反正就是能够减少梯度下降过程中的走的弯路就行。"}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "70 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/603468895"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4IrOHz2YmPu9ljEAMaCDk2Mzg0NzM3IKWjy6MGMAA4TUAGcgk2MDM0Njg4OTV4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "7_1685991712.9864783", "card_id": "Q_604742928", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 10}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "皇马前场大洗牌，本泽马、阿森西奥、阿扎尔等离队，你认为皇马会引进哪些新援，哪些球员适合皇马呢？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "67 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/604742928"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4IrOHz2YmPu9ljEAMaCDk2NjY3NDg1II/N8aMGMAA4EUAHcgk2MDQ3NDI5Mjh4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "8_1685991712.9870067", "card_id": "Q_604432723", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 37}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "6 月 5 日是「世界环境日」，你理想中人与自然的关系是怎样的？为此我们可以做些什么？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-806040620e820b6d194a4cc44ad724a2_720w.webp?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "63 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/604432723"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4IrOHz2YmPu9ljEAMaCDk2NTk4NTYxIKvn5qMGMAE4PkAIcgk2MDQ0MzI3MjN4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "9_1685991712.9876814", "card_id": "